    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine, and the interior is pristine, showing absolutely no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine is incredibly smooth and powerful, while the transmission shifts seamlessly. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a car in peak original condition with all maintenance records up to date.",
