    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very dependable; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts cleanly through all gears. While the exterior and interior show some light signs of regular use, such as minor surface scratches or small upholstery wear, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and fully functional. It is a solid choice for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that has many miles left to offer.",
      "price": 33500.0,
