      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated to an exacting standard, preserved in showroom condition with no discernible wear to the interior or exterior. Every component reflects a commitment to mechanical excellence, offering the discerning enthusiast a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example. A comprehensive inspection will confirm its status as an investment-grade asset for any collection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
